    "pages.authorityGuidePages.calciumIsEssentialForBone": "Calcium is essentiel for bone integrity, muscle contraction, blood clotting, and nerve transmission. Ionized (gratuit) calcium is the physiologically actif form. Always vérifier albumin niveaux — for every 1 g/dL decrease in albumin, total calcium decreases by approximately 0.8 mg/dL (corrected calcium calculation).",
