    "pages.authorityGuidePages.confusionLethargyHeadacheNauseavomitingSe": "Confusion, lethargy, headache, nausea/vomiting, seizures (severe), cerebral œdème. Symptômes correlate with évaluer of refuser — aigu onset is plus dangerous than chronique.",
    "pages.authorityGuidePages.confusionSeizuresThinkSodiumOr": "(confusion, seizures) → think sodium or severe calcium imbalance",
