    "pages.authorityGuidePages.focusedAssessmentsAreTargetedEvaluations": "Focused assessments are targeted evaluations performed when you know (or suspect) a spécifique condition. Examen questions often present a Scénario clinique and ask \"Which évaluation is the priorité?\" Knowing the focused évaluation for each condition is essentiel.",
