    "pages.authorityGuidePages.oftenConsideredThe5thVital": "Often considered the \"5th vital signer.\" Use appropriate scale for patient population.",
    "pages.authorityGuidePages.onDocumentationQuestionsChooseThe": "Activé documentation questions, choisir the most objectif, spécifique, and measurable option. Avoid réponses that inclure infirmier opinions, subjective interpretations, or vague conditions like \"bon,\" \"normal,\" or \"improved\" without measurable criteria.",
    "pages.authorityGuidePages.opioidOverdoseAdministerNaloxoneNarcan": "Opioid overdose: administrer naloxone (Narcan) — moniteur for re-sedation",
    "pages.authorityGuidePages.opioidsedativeOverdosePneumothoraxAirwayObs": "Opioid/sedative overdose, pneumothorax, voies aériennes obstruction, neuromuscular maladie (Guillain-Barré, myasthenia gravis), severe asthma, pneumonia, ARDS, anesthesia",
    "pages.authorityGuidePages.oralCalciumSupplementsWithVitamin": "Oral calcium supplements with vitamin D for chronique gestion",
