    "pages.authorityGuidePages.rate1220minDepthPatternRegular": "Évaluer (12-20/min), depth, modèle (regular, Cheyne-Stokes, Kussmaul, Biot's), use of accessory muscles, chest symmetry",
    "pages.authorityGuidePages.readTheLabValuesCarefully": "Lire the Valeurs de laboratoire carefully. Identifier which Électrolyte is anormal and whether it is élevé or faible. Many étudiants make erreurs because they focus activé the Scénario clinique before checking the labs.",
