    "pages.nursingClinicalScenariosHub.wbc13500lCrpElevatedBnp": "WBC 13,500/μL, CRP elevated, BNP 45 pg/mL (normal).",
    "pages.nursingClinicalScenariosHub.wbc18200lLactate38Mmoll": "WBC 18,200/μL, lactate 3.8 mmol/L, creatinine 1.6 mg/dL (référence 0.9), glucose 245 mg/dL, procalcitonin 4.2 ng/mL.",
