    "pages.nursingSkillChecklistsHub.stepbystepNursingSkillChecklistsFor": "Étape-by-étape infirmier compétence checklists for IV insertion, central line soins, plaie dressing changes, oxygène thérapie setup, and blood transfusion. Includes infirmier justification, sécurité alertes, and NCLEX Préparation à l'examen notes.",
