    "pages.perioperativeHubPages.thePreoperativePhaseIsThe": "The préopératoire phase is the most heavily tested domaine activé the CNOR examen. Focus activé patient évaluation workflows, chirurgical site marking protocols, informed consent exigences, and NPO guidelines. Remember: the circulating infirmier(ère) is responsible for verifying tous elements of the pre-procédure vérification processus.",
